# Design Document: Alpha Insights - Stock Portfolio Tracker

## 1. Project Overview
- **Application:** Alpha Insights - AI-Powered Stock Portfolio Tracker
- **Description:** A sophisticated, dark-themed stock portfolio management application with glassmorphic UI, real-time market data, and AI-driven insights.
- **Target Tech Stack:** React 18, TypeScript, Vite, TailwindCSS v3, Recharts, Flask Backend

