## 3. Page Layout & Structure

### Global Layout
- **Overall Layout:** Single-page application with route-based navigation
- **Navigation:** Sticky top navigation bar with glassmorphic styling
- **Background:** Deep slate-900 with subtle gradient overlays
- **Container:** Max-width responsive containers with proper padding

### Navigation Structure
- **Public Routes:** Landing Page, Login, Signup, Education Hub
- **Protected User Routes:** Dashboard, Portfolio, Stock Research, Notifications, Profile Settings
- **Protected Admin Routes:** Admin Dashboard, User Management, System Settings

